      "text": "<p>Element <code>#box-container</code> mora imati svojstvo <code>flex-direction</code> postavljeno na <code>row-reverse</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "const boxContainer = document.querySelector('#box-container');\r\nconst flexDirection = window.getComputedStyle(boxContainer)['flex-direction'];\r\nassert.strictEqual(flexDirection, 'row-reverse');"
    }
